data.title: Lonnie⛸
data.content: It’s jasmine season again!!🦒 the whole world feels like it has a great energy at the moment and i think it must be a season of renewal (also 6 planets are in retrograde right now!! So things are intense in a really good way)🌷🌷all the things I’ve been dreaming about this year are coming true and it’s absolutely fantastic: I was gonna also say it’s summer dress season again but if I’m being real with you that’s every month of the year with me🌵🌺🌵 #newselfwales
